{"tid":1652683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌曬你地班連登仔 仆街","createTime":"2019-10-13T18:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T19:34:57.000Z","uid":122272,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"efb74d1a55f52a3eee52a847721d1cbe12b95303","tid":1652683,"uid":122272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T18:16:28.000Z","msg":"喂 文宣啊仆街 之前果張又話亂 呢張整到咁都唔share岀去 抵比人屌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日有不反對集會啊 唔係唔去啊？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mq28tmc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMq28tmc.png&h=df5378e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3yXwq78.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3yXwq78.png&h=2a68cb32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日七點遮打見！"},{"pid":"060f192de99939732753e66b0c2c3aa563dde6d3","tid":1652683,"uid":124048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T18:22:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1G4yEvn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1G4yEvn.jpg&h=0f9223d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聽晚1900遮打花園嘅集會係合法嘅，跪求大家一定要去<br />\n‼️//依家有2個重量級人馬過黎香港視察(Ted Cruz, Josh David Hawley), 而Donald Trump 亦講過香港示威少左人，暗示香港需要搞一次大型既集會/遊行。‼️<br />\n聽日係展現香港人想美國推人權及民主法案既決心，到時兩位都會在場，班狗無得亂黎，無不反都要出，射盲眼，性侵，被自殺等已經忍無可忍，香港人反抗!//<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cf2db3a6bd4dc285dd51edd93338e7b10eed701","tid":1652683,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T18:22:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3e3fceeb6ad0b0aca242c27ae7c8754b272d70e","tid":1652683,"uid":122272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T18: